name: Semi Wormhole
description: This work is a beautiful representation of Space,Time, Wormhole, Alien live and The Universe... It features far away stars and galaxies, the vast darkness in space, An unclear planet, the far greenish glow representing Aliens, the brightest star and an impaired vision of Look hole representing the wormhole... This work entails more than you can see at a glance,more than what is listed here.
